snippet.textDisplay:
Shiraz Uppal was always a spiritual person. His sheer belief put him in close friendship with A.R. Rehman so much so that 
A.R. invited him to sing with him in 2012 in New York which he did. It was a wonderful combination(a MUST SEE )

 Shiraz has many more spirituals to be manifested in the years to come. We pray for him. His late dad was a close friend who, sadly,  died in an helicopter crash being its captain in the dreadful Lahore fog.  I am  sure he is proud of his son up there.
